      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 15,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 15:4",
      "text": "ܘܕܐܬܩܒܪ ܘܩܡ ܠܬܠܬܐ ܝܘܡܝܢ ܐܝܟ ܕܟܬܝܒ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
