      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 15,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 15:5",
      "text": "ܘܐܬܚܙܝ ܠܟܐܦܐ ܘܒܬܪܗ ܠܬܪܥܤܪ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
